<item>
            <title>[HBASE-936] REST Interface:   enable to get numbers of rows from scanner interface</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-936</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The scanner request will return one row for each request defaultly. But due to reduce the network bandwidth also the usability of the api, it should allow return multiple rows at once.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
